## File Structure

| Path | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `src/app/api/` | API routes (all use Supabase) |
| `src/components/` | React components |
| `src/lib/db.ts` | Database client (Supabase) |
| `src/types/` | TypeScript types |
| `supabase/migrations/` | Database migrations |
| `supabase/config.toml` | Supabase CLI config |

---

## Quick Start Commands

```bash
bun install    # Install dependencies
bun run dev    # Start development server
```

No database setup required - `.env` is pre-configured.

---

## Environment

The `.env` file is committed and contains live Supabase credentials:

```
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://uosbndvnjposzpbtvhvq.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJhbG...
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=eyJhbG...
```

Do NOT modify database connection settings without explicit permission.
